title: Dance Dance Danseur
synopsis: Junpei is happily snoozing away during his sister's ballet recital when a male ballet dancer steps onto the stage. Moved by the strength and skills the dancer displays, the boy discovers his love for this art.
staff: [['Sakai, Munehisa', ['Director']], ['George, Asakura', ['Original Creator']], ['Narita, Yoshimi', ['Series Composition']], ['Hasegawa, Hitomi', ['Character Design']]]
